{"id":"vis17.r3.i2.n05","recik":null,"parent":null,"source":"VS","author":"AJ","tags":["T04","F04","D4","M03","P2","N2"],"title":null,"content":[{"sl":"Za eksponentno porazdeljeno slučajno spremenljivko $X$,
